But when Audrey, a younger and prettier woman, is hired instead, it proves too much for Constance to take.","genre_ids":[53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2259,"vote_count":123,"poster_path":"/oS7NwVS2Rm5jJT3YudiOrRUCOSO.jpg","release_date":"2016-07-06","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/rbPXJdrlp6zssYttuaUlpAoypk6.jpg","original_title":"Irréprochable","original_language":"fr"},{"id":529207,"adult":false,"title":"Crime Wave","video":false,"overview":"Leyre lives a quiet and comfortable life which ends abruptly when an act of rage of her teenage son leads her to protect him by any means necessary.","genre_ids":[35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3528,"vote_count":100,"poster_path":"/6iK0eUBcBVT2LkcFXVpMB8gz92e.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-04","vote_average":5.785,"backdrop_path":"/k7GNUAh4YjVIT1xlqKjdyT4HQLD.jpg","original_title":"Ola de crímenes","original_language":"es"},{"id":222772,"adult":false,"title":"Lion's Heart","video":false,"overview":"Ivana Cornejo is just getting used to being single again after her divorce three years ago. After an exasperating call from her ex-husband, she throws her cell phone away. Fortunately, the man who finds it calls her to return it, and to her amusement they have an instant rapport. The man on the other end of the phone is León Godoy, a renowned architect with a charming voice and a charismatic personality. They schedule a date so that he can return the cell phone. When León arrives, Ivana is surprised: he is everything she had imagined, except for one unexpected and startling detail... he’s only 4'5\" tall.","genre_ids":[35,10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2939,"vote_count":116,"poster_path":"/mnGZ6VPB7T923oLDGChcPdzmZxk.jpg","release_date":"2013-08-15","vote_average":6.78,"backdrop_path":"/47PuJrRvu3jNeuSbeks5kN9dHPd.jpg","original_title":"Corazón de león","original_language":"es"},{"id":14019,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Drummer","video":false,"overview":"Three musicians form a band. But they're not just any musicians: each has a disability that makes them particularly unsuitable for their instrument. The guitarist is deaf, the singer is tone deaf, and the bassist has a stiff arm. They lack a drummer, and to respect the group's uniqueness, they turn to a famous writer who has never played the drums. He accepts, but begins a manipulation that will wreak further havoc on the already largely dysfunctional band.","genre_ids":[35,80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5919,"vote_count":234,"poster_path":"/7VxXp2h9UtJP6XbeuQGqqbQzoE1.jpg","release_date":"2007-01-31","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/mIYSIgQjTU0Y7e1yZ08E588A8av.jpg","original_title":"Ex Drummer","original_language":"nl"}],"similar_content":[{"id":79,"adult":false,"title":"Hero","video":false,"overview":"During China's Warring States period, a district prefect arrives at the palace of Qin Shi Huang, claiming to have killed the three assassins who had made an attempt on the king's life three years ago.","genre_ids":[18,12,28,36],"popularity":7.13,"vote_count":2436,"poster_path":"/vxgZto2Cz7ILHAlmRXt50I2brB2.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-19","vote_average":7.508,"backdrop_path":"/jDz6RYN3nKYtlo7J9IMvGoJit7B.jpg","original_title":"英雄","original_language":"zh"},{"id":144,"adult":false,"title":"Wings of Desire","video":false,"overview":"Two angels, Damiel and Cassiel, glide through the streets of Berlin, observing the bustling population, providing invisible rays of hope to the distressed but never interacting with them. When Damiel falls in love with lonely trapeze artist Marion, the angel longs to experience life in the physical world, and finds — with some words of wisdom from actor Peter Falk — that it might be possible for him to take human form.","genre_ids":[18,14,10749],"popularity":4.7249,"vote_count":1464,"poster_path":"/iZQs2vUeCzvS1KfZJ6uYNCGJBBV.jpg","release_date":"1987-09-23","vote_average":7.768,"backdrop_path":"/7TlGXrB4WQ3wbpOCUQnBXseCuOl.jpg","original_title":"Der Himmel über Berlin","original_language":"de"},{"id":150,"adult":false,"title":"48 Hrs.","video":false,"overview":"A hard-nosed cop reluctantly teams up with a wise-cracking criminal temporarily paroled to him, in order to track down a killer.","genre_ids":[80,28,35],"popularity":3.8124,"vote_count":1659,"poster_path":"/rvvjXHzEDBIvIVDBHNOwHS7hVPu.jpg","release_date":"1982-12-07","vote_average":6.675,"backdrop_path":"/xQTSGz5dvIAYFssPWhD160AcR7Z.jpg","original_title":"48 Hrs.","original_language":"en"},{"id":205,"adult":false,"title":"Hotel Rwanda","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by true events, this film takes place in Rwanda in the 1990s when more than a million Tutsis were killed in a genocide that went mostly unnoticed by the rest of the world. Hotel owner Paul Rusesabagina houses over a thousand refuges in his hotel in attempt to save their lives.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":3.3744,"vote_count":3096,"poster_path":"/p3pHw85UMZPegfMZBA6dZ06yarm.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-22","vote_average":7.715,"backdrop_path":"/jkvvXaN7FPVKGlk8oj9PL0FHNtj.jpg","original_title":"Hotel Rwanda","original_language":"en"},{"id":207,"adult":false,"title":"Dead Poets Society","video":false,"overview":"At an elite, old-fashioned boarding school in New England, a passionate English teacher inspires his students to rebel against convention and seize the potential of every day, courting the disdain of the stern headmaster.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":12.8965,"vote_count":12322,"poster_path":"/l5NbiHKUmahlAT3Q1ig8Tyl9xrc.jpg","release_date":"1989-06-02","vote_average":8.301,"backdrop_path":"/yYvBNN96Ym3wtPxGCFl7F888WwB.jpg","original_title":"Dead Poets Society","original_language":"en"},{"id":271394,"adult":false,"title":"El caso Laura","video":false,"overview":"Laura abandons her peaceful life as a doctor to avenge her sister, who was cheated by a band of pornographers who drugged her to film her rape.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2127,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/sbNJAJXV6