s of cleaning up the filthy city.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":14.2872,"vote_count":13213,"poster_path":"/ekstpH614fwDX8DUln1a2Opz0N8.jpg","release_date":"1976-02-09","vote_average":8.127,"backdrop_path":"/9uddYYTNcLWpzUkl5iw1RUYhLhY.jpg","original_title":"Taxi Driver","original_language":"en"},{"id":115,"adult":false,"title":"The Big Lebowski","video":false,"overview":"Jeffrey 'The Dude' Lebowski, a Los Angeles slacker who only wants to bowl and drink White Russians, is mistaken for another Jeffrey Lebowski, a wheelchair-bound millionaire, and finds himself dragged into a strange series of events involving nihilists, adult film producers, ferrets, errant toes, and large sums of money.","genre_ids":[35,80],"popularity":9.1537,"vote_count":11962,"poster_path":"/9mprbw31MGdd66LR0AQKoDMoFRv.jpg","release_date":"1998-03-06","vote_average":7.839,"backdrop_path":"/hXsy4XCCHrUk81XoRhcooyWejao.jpg","original_title":"The Big Lebowski","original_language":"en"},{"id":261,"adult":false,"title":"Cat on a Hot Tin Roof","video":false,"overview":"An alcoholic ex-football player drinks his days away, having failed to come to terms with his sexuality and his real feelings for his football buddy who died after an ambiguous accident. His wife is crucified by her desperation to make him desire her: but he resists the affections of his wife. His reunion with his father—who is dying of cancer—jogs a host of memories and revelations for both father and son.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.1895,"vote_count":819,"poster_path":"/5djZZECgqDGuSI1INmrdAcGRBb0.jpg","release_date":"1958-08-29","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/3Yz8IcUBPZ8zDff0ktHZk24Rot0.jpg","original_title":"Cat on a Hot Tin Roof","original_language":"en"},{"id":274,"adult":false,"title":"The Silence of the Lambs","video":false,"overview":"Clarice Starling is a top student at the FBI's training academy.  Jack Crawford wants Clarice to interview Dr. Hannibal Lecter, a brilliant psychiatrist who is also a violent psychopath, serving life behind bars for various acts of murder and cannibalism.  Crawford believes that Lecter may have insight into a case and that Starling, as an attractive young woman, may be just the bait to draw him out.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"popularity":5.0881,"vote_count":17611,"poster_path":"/uS9m8OBk1A8eM9I042bx8XXpqAq.jpg","release_date":"1991-02-14","vote_average":8.346,"backdrop_path":"/aYcnDyLMnpKce1FOYUpZrXtgUye.jpg","original_title":"The Silence of the Lambs","original_language":"en"},{"id":275,"adult":false,"title":"Fargo","video":false,"overview":"Jerry, a small-town Minnesota car salesman is bursting at the seams with debt... but he's got a plan. He's going to hire two thugs to kidnap his wife in a scheme to collect a hefty ransom from his wealthy father-in-law. It's going to be a snap and nobody's going to get hurt... until people start dying. Enter Police Chief Marge, a coffee-drinking, parka-wearing - and extremely pregnant - investigator who'll stop at nothing to get her man. And if you think her small-time investigative skills will give the crooks a run for their ransom... you betcha!","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":8.6528,"vote_count":8901,"poster_path":"/rt7cpEr1uP6RTZykBFhBTcRaKvG.jpg","release_date":"1996-03-08","vote_average":7.847,"backdrop_path":"/747dgDfL5d8esobk7h4odaOFhUq.jpg","original_title":"Fargo","original_language":"en"},{"id":276,"adult":false,"title":"The Edukators","video":false,"overview":"Three activists cobble together a kidnapping plot after they encounter a businessman in his home.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.8087,"vote_count":371,"poster_path":"/jpiXFtvBYemLbAktLPNx5xDGvJn.jpg","release_date":"2004-10-25","vote_average":7.155,"backdrop_path":"/whgmJ6vRE7o8zszh60kicT1vVSy.jpg","original_title":"Die fetten Jahre sind vorbei","original_language":"de"},{"id":186,"adult":false,"title":"Lucky Number Slevin","video":false,"overview":"Slevin is mistakenly put in the middle of a personal war between the city’s biggest criminal bosses. Under constant watch, Slevin must try not to get killed by an infamous assassin and come up with an idea of how to get out of his current dilemma.","genre_ids":[18,53,80,9648],"popularity":4.8949,"vote_count":4367,"poster_path":"/x21s3p5wPww534nYj1cWakTcqz4.jpg","release_date":"2006-02-24","vote_average":7.477,"backdrop_path":"/ShDHEWiJ4NL6ldn4W2m3bEkIBr.jpg","original_title":"Lucky Number Slevin","original_language":"en"},{"id":187,"adult":false,"title":"Sin City","video":false,"overview":"Welcome to Sin City. This town beckons to the tough, the corrupt, the brokenhearted. Some call it dark… Hard-boiled. Then there are those who call it home — Crooked cops, sexy dames, desperate vigilantes. Some are seeking revenge, others lust after redemption, and then there are those hoping for a little of both. A universe of unlikely and reluctant heroes still trying to do the right thing in a city that refuses to care.","genre_ids":[80,53],"popularity":5.9662,"vote_count":8681,"poster_path":"/i66G50wATMmPrvpP95f0XP6ZdVS.jpg","release_date":"2005-04-01","vote_average":7.463,"backdrop_path":"/t9kQnqiaxQ8TLB25rTzDKLd0fdM.jpg","original_title":"Sin City","original_language":"en"},{"id":235,"adult":false,"title":"Stand by Me","video":false,"overview":"After learning that a boy their age has been accidentally killed near their rural homes, four boys decide to go see the body. Gordie, Vern, Chris, and Teddy encounter a mean junk man and a marsh full of leeches, but they also learn more about one another and their very different home lives. Just a lark at first, the boys' adventure evolves into a defining event in their lives.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":7.5425,"vote_count":6358,"poster_path":"/vz0w9BSehcqjDcJOjRaCk7fgJe7.jpg","release_date":"1986-08-08","vote_average":7.843,"backdrop_path":"/yjGllQUm28R4X9xD9T5xMszirgw.jpg","original_title":"Stand by Me","original_language":"en"},{"id":238,"adult":false,"title":"The Godfather","video":false,"overview":"Spanning the years 1945 to 1955, a chronicle of the fictional Italian-American Corleone crime family. When organized crime family patriarch, Vito Corleone barely survives an attempt on his life, his youngest son, Michael steps in to take care of the would-be killers, launching a campaign of bloody revenge.","genre_ids":[18,80],"popularity":41.0892,"vote_count":22509,"poster_path":"/3bhkrj58Vtu7enYsRolD1fZdja1.jpg","release_date":"1972-03-14","vote_average":8.7,"backdrop_path":"/tSPT36ZKlP2WVHJLM4cQPLSzv3b.jpg","original_title":"The Godfather","original_language":"en"},{"id":271410,"adult":false,"title":"Duvarların Ötesi","video":false,"overview":"A story of 7 prisoners who sentenced to death for kidnapping a rich businessman's daughter.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":1.4834,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/sV6TVtto39nthloCzvyQPO3cptV.jpg","release_date":"1964-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/4mTVTlI9QhRAPwQW1SCClk0P8VI.jpg","original_title":"Duvarların Ötesi","original_language":"tr"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt4411504","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q18709329","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/the-clan","mydramalist_id":"280277","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/the_clan_2016"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148755,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AE","release_dates":[{"note":"Dubai International Film Festival","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2015-12-12T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2015-08-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"16"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BG","release_dates":[{"note":"Sofia International Film Festival","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2016-